{"tid":1451250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 經過今日之後，首要做既事就係「捉鬼」","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:30:04.000Z","uid":167177,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8da089b2930bee7a534a6c9bac2d20cc165d499a","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:31.000Z","msg":"發夢由於好多狗隻時常出現橫行在你我之間，捉又捉唔到，所以大家要由三個方面去思考：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 大眾層面</span></strong><br />\n當一大班人一齊時，要如何確定身邊的人是否有內鬼。<br />\n可以靠<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">外型、裝束、髮型</span></strong></span>等去觀察。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我希望自己友唔好因被懷疑係內奸而敵視自己人，反而以手足有捉鬼既決心為榮！</span></span></strong></span></span><br />\ne.g. 即場驗手機、查袋、查銀包、搜身等<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.小隊層面</span></strong><br />\n如本身已是小隊，要確定有沒有成員係鬼。<br />\n方法主要靠自己圍內溝通決定。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由於已有鬼潛伏在內，所以有必要重新double check過。</span></span></strong><br />\ne.g.自己友有獨特logo、卡套、電話聆聲等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.社交媒體層面</span></strong><br />\nTg、連登、高登基本上好多鬼，後兩者其實好難捉。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以Tg細gp捉內鬼係必要同緊急！</span></span></strong><br />\n要點捉，就要用自己方法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>總之，捉鬼係<span style=\"color: red;\">首要</span>大任務，<br />\n唔好輕易相信身邊既扮友善或唔起眼既手足(真Friend除外)，包括埋開Post既我！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎集合大家思維討論，各施各法！"},{"pid":"44663734762bf5b875d7cf93472c01dbe2b3f33d","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:39:24.000Z","msg":"自推10下<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"00b7af79e96e73aa74af92a564c8bac3c5d7e6db","tid":1451250,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:41:14.000Z","msg":"人地開到囗叫麻包袋喇"},{"pid":"f57a145f494587ae37dea5c7477ea8720632d35e","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b7af79e96e73aa74af92a564c8bac3c5d7e6db","tid":1451250,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:41:14.000Z","msg":"人地開到囗叫麻包袋喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:42:38.000Z","msg":"你都要搵到出黎先用到麻包袋"},{"pid":"4d4641d1a314d002f1e365177d3515c002458dc2","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"631fe602bd5519535286388ec968eae4bb2684e3","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"efc249c813ec1f019f6b1dbceb71bf04356e7c15","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:47:31.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"05bf07d8d83ca48c6bd085b50df7e3d98781cc17","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:50:59.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"d9e8e71e4639fb150ca0006cb88520df608c4bb4","tid":1451250,"uid":241132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"佢地今次有耳筒, 但下次可能用暗號"},{"pid":"1908dd7b756dd7553a5d332795c87ab89ef5abd0","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e8e71e4639fb150ca0006cb88520df608c4bb4","tid":1451250,"uid":241132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:58:54.000Z","msg":"佢地今次有耳筒, 但下次可能用暗號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"所以要先鞏固自己圍內人唔係鬼，再推出去檢驗當場有無人係鬼"},{"pid":"6fda03940c7e3b6ac5311bc7eeea6a999acfc95b","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"0f5617c78a3caa410bfb7de986c0fa45ad04c7dd","tid":1451250,"uid":167177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"